ill reflect the clients we serve and the communities we work in, so if you&rsquo;re excited about this role but your past experience doesn&rsquo;t align perfectly with every qualification in the job description we encourage you to apply anyways. You may be just the right candidate for this or other roles.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;STV offers the following benefits &bull; Health insurance, including an option with a Health Savings Account &bull; Dental insurance &bull; Vision insurance &bull; Flexible Spending Accounts (Healthcare, Dependent Care and Transit and Parking where applicable) &bull; Disability insurance &bull; Life Insurance and Accidental Death &amp;amp; Dismemberment &bull; 401(k) Plan &bull; Retirement Counseling &bull; Employee Assistance Program &bull; Paid Time Off (16 days) &bull; Paid Holidays (8 days) &bull; Back-Up Dependent Care (up to 10 days per year) &bull; Parental Leave (up to 80 hours) &bull; Continuing Education Program &bull; Professional Licensure and Society Memberships&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;STV is committed to paying all its employees in a fair, equitable, and transparent manner. The listed pay range is STV&rsquo;s good-faith salary estimates this position. Please note that the final salary offered for this position may be outside of this published range based on many factors, including but not limited to geography, education, experience, and/or certifications.&lt;/p&gt;', 1, 'Electrical Engineering', 'FULL TIME', '104601', '136695', '&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: revert; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica