(30, 'Honeywell International', 'New York, NY', 'Mechanical Engineer- Transit Facilities', '&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;TYLin is a globally recognized, full-service infrastructure consulting firm committed to providing innovative, cost-effective, constructible designs for the global infrastructure market. With over 3,000 employees throughout the Americas, Asia, and Europe, the firm provides support on projects of varying size and complexity. Together, we enhance conventional designs with smarter, more resilient systems. We provide people with better mobility. We steward precious resources by finding more sustainable solutions.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;Job Summary&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We are seeking a Senior Mechanical Engineer/Inspector for our PMCM Sector to work on various Infrastructure/Transit projects. This position will report to the Lead Mechanical Engineer and will require at least 5+ years of experience in mechanical design, inspection, and commissioning of transportation facilities and/or other building systems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;Responsibilities &amp;amp; Qualifications&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Conduct mechanical systems design including, but not limited to, HVAC/R, pump systems, boilers, duct design, airflow distribution and balancing, etc.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Review mechanical systems plans, shop drawings and approved submittals for design and construction.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Perform mechanical systems inspections of contractor operations for conformance to plans, proposals and specifications.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Perform mechanical systems and equipment testing. Ensure compliance with approved equipment/specs.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Reviewing site conditions, and equipment installation.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Write detailed daily inspection reports including in site measurements, as-built sketches, quantity calculations and tracking of manpower/resources.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Advise senior staff of potential deficiencies in field conditions and overruns.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Scheduled shifts may vary and may include nights and weekend work.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;QUALIFICATIONS:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Mechanical Engineering required.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Minimum 5+ years of experience in design and inspection of Mechanical, Electrical, and Plumbing (MEP) facilities-related projects.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Experience with NYC Municipalities preferred.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Considerable knowledge of construction materials and methods required.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Ability to read plans/specs and prepare written contract administration documentation such as daily narratives (work reports), controlled inspection reports, daily time and material records.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Must be able to document unit price work, keep track of work in place totals for all items of work including contract work, unit price work, extra work, and time and material work on a daily basis.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Strong oral and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Working knowledge of Microsoft Office Suite particularly Word, Excel and Site Manager.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Additional Information&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;If this is a safety-sensitive role subject to the Code of Federal Regulations (49 CFR Part 219). As such, you understand that as a condition of employment, this role requires you to complete and pass both pre-employment and other screenings in accordance with the law.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;TYLin is committed to pay equity. As part of that commitment, we have provided the base compensation range of $86,300 - $130,900 annually for this position and local market. We recognize that each candidate brings a unique set of skills, experience, education and competencies to the table that will be reflected in our offer. TYLin is proud to offer exciting career development opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;TYLin offers a comprehensive total rewards package. Our benefits include extensive medical, disability and life insurance coverage, continuing education benefits, paid time off, employee assistance program and a retirement savings plan with company matching contributions.&lt;/p&gt;', 1, 'Mechanical Engineering', 'FULL TIME', '98700', '156000', '&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: revert; color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; padding: revert; display: revert; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: inherit; margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Mechanical Engineering required.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: inherit; margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Minimum 5+ years of experience in design and inspection of Mechanical, Electrical, and Plumbing (MEP) facilities-related projects.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: inherit; margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Experience with NYC Municipalities preferred.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: inherit; margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Considerable knowledge of construction materials and methods required.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: inherit; margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Ability to read plans/specs and prepare written contract administration documentation such as daily narratives (work reports), controlled inspection reports, daily time and material records.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: inherit; margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Must be able to document unit price work, keep track of work in place totals for all items of work including contract work, unit price work, extra work, and time and material work on a daily basis.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: inherit; margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Strong oral and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: inherit; margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Working knowledge of Microsoft Office Suite particularly Word, Excel and Site Manager.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', '3', '2024-02-29', '2024-02-01 20:51:52');
