t-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Prepare technical specifications, review and sign-off on calculations and prepare construction documents&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Work closely with clients, architects, other Buro Happold Engineers, and/or design team members as part of a dedicated and skilled team&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Communicate directly with Clients&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Manage workload of Project Discipline Engineers (including verification of quality)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Take responsibility for concept and preliminary engineering solutions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Carry out design reviews prior to the issue of technical documentation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Monitor financial performance of projects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Under guidance of senior staff, represent Buro Happold at meetings with the client, other professionals and suppliers.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Set up and manage job/project administrative systems, including planning and monitoring job resourcing/expenditure (adjusting these as necessary)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Keep senior staff informed of important and relevant service/design decisions and the objectives of the client are achieved&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Continually ensure practices, policies, strategy and services represent the client&rsquo;s best interests and that Buro Happold policy is in keeping with current legislation and the relevant building codes for the relevant state etc&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: revert; padding: revert; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;What are we looking for?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; caret-color: rgb(45, 45, 45); color: rgb(45, 45, 45);&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;6+ years of experience in Mechanical Engineering and HVAC experience&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Ability to accept a high degree of responsibility in a team-based organization, combined with ability to work independently&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Broad Mechanical Engineering and Environmental design knowledge, from working on a wide range of US and international projects&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: revert; padding: revert; display: revert; list-style-type: disc; font-size: inherit; font-family: &amp;quot;Noto Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;&quot;&gt;Ideally sector experience in Cultural projects, Labs, Commercial and Higher Education&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;